Tiny basement with a low ceiling just high enough for a mini-moonboard.

At 40°, It features moon yellow holds and many more wooden or plastic grips including some DIY. Extremely awful sitstarts and evil crux matching top await, all logged in a lovely binder.

Contact me @lasagna_lats on instagram if you want to session!
